            <h3 class="display-3">Documentation</h3>
            <hr>
            <section class="container-fluid" id="overview">
                <h4 class="display-4">Overview</h4>
                <p>
                    <abbr title="Which means light in French">Lumi√®re</abbr> is
                    a standalone <abbr title="Software as a service">SaaS</abbr> that provides a simple way for small &amp;
                    medium businesses to handle with verifying the authenticity of
                    a media file that relates to human verification.
                </p>
                <p>
                    In the current release, this product is solely capable of performing
                    the validation as a helper, which means, all auxiliary data
                    such as user ID, personal information,... is not handled by this product.
                    This also means that this service is only capable of verifying
                    whether or not a media file is forged with help of an AI tool.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our planned release is to enable more functionalities such as
                    authentication, in-depth analysis and threat intellignence,...
                    For the mean time, please enjoy the service!
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="container-fluid" id="api">
                <h4 class="display-4">APIs</h4>
                <p>
                    Our product provides a collection of APIs that supports human
                    verficiation over voice and face detection.
                </p>
